node.text:
Understanding different asset classes can be key for long-term success

For beginners, @Robbywclark recommends matching your liability expenses with your asset purchases💰

Here's Robby's breakdown of different asset classes he likes for long-term success:

1. Real estate. Buy a property and rent it out. That’ll help pay down equity while also having a consistent cash flow🏡

2. Stocks are a traditional investment vehicle. Historically they tend to be a safe investment over the long run that will accumulate big returns over time.

3. I love cryptocurrencies, but to an old-school investor they would be considered risky, so limit your exposure when starting, but don’t miss out!

4. Whole/universal life insurance policies can also be a great investment vehicle and are utilized by savvy investors as well as ultra-high network individuals to invest in their future

@TheIdealCard No Contact Networking Cards

@TheIdealCard The Smartest Business Card In The World
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
@TheIdealCard Smart Contactless #DigitalBusinessCards by @INKGILITY
⁣⁣
The Reinvention of the #BusinessCard is Finally Here thanks to @INKGILITY⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
Tap into the Future of #BusinessCards with @TheIdealCard, A Smart #Contactless #DigitalBusinessCard for The Digital Age.⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
@TheIdealCard is a chip embedded instrument that triggers an Add to Contacts action on Compatible #Smartphones such as an #iPhone & #Android phone displaying voluminous, just transferred contact details in a matter of seconds.⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
You can transfer details such as your Name, Company Name, A Photo or Logo, Email Address, Phone Number(s), Website, Physical Address with directions from Google Maps, Social Media Profiles & Instant Messaging Profiles, Payment Profiles, Emergency Contact Information, Videos, Music, Shopping Pages, an Elevator Pitch, Upcoming Events, and much more.⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
@TheIdealCard comes as a card, ring, key holder, wallet, smartphone sticky, and many more items for added convenience.⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣Developed by @INKGILITY, The World’s Most Innovative Marketing Company & Largest Selection of #BusinessCards @INKGILITY

for newcomers getting started:

1. Get started

2. Energy goes where revenue flows-If you’re gonna spend $200 on shoes, the bar, a handbag, then invest $200 in stocks or another asset. Match your liability expenses with assets purchases

3. No excuses. I went from bankruptcy to 9-figures in assets. Create good habits & learn daily

If you’re new to the game of investing, nows your time to get started. Let’s get it👊

node.text: The Gulfstream #G500 — the aircraft that led business travel into a new era — and the only aircraft in its class with a high-speed cruise of Mach. 0.90. Watch to experience the #ArtOfExcellence.

@jacobandco presents its latest collaboration with @alecmonopoly to bring you the Jacob & Co Astronomia Alec Monopoly 🔥🎨

The process behind creating these characters begin as drawings which become CAD renderings and perfectly sized to fit inside the watch and finally cast in gold, and hand finished. 🤯

This collaboration further prooves just how versatile and innovative @Jacobandco is. From high jewelry masterpieces to collaborations with iconoc movies, hyper-cars and now internatially renown artists! 

Swipe to see what @alecmonopoly has to say about this stunning timepiece! @jacobandco @alecmonopoly #TheBillionairesClub

node.text:
Have you seen this beautiful timepiece yet?
 
@Skeletonconceptofficial skeletonized the very complex GMT-MASTER II “Batman” and the result is mesmerizing!
 
The #KimpembeConcept is sportswear and fashionable. The bi-color bezel fiving more allure and contrast to the whole gray matte Oyster steel timepiece.
 
Named after the French champion of the 2018 football World Cup and @psg player, @kimpembe3 in person participated in the creating process of this stunning timepiece.
 
This timepiece is one of our summer favorites.
 
________
Skeleton Concept is a handcraft atelier that specializes in watch customization.
They neither manufacture and/or sell timepieces. Skeleton Concept is not affiliated, associated, authorized, endorsed by, or in any way officially connected with RoleX SA or any of its subsidiaries.  The personalization of the watches are carried out meticulously while staying true to the essence of the original brand manufacturers. Skeleton Concept assures the integrity of the work and modifications made on behalf of its clients and their timepieces. Any and all the customizations made are for the personal and private use of the owners only

node.text:
🚨 New Launch Alert!! 🚨 @jacobandco presents its latest collaboration with @alecmonopoly to bring you the Jacob & Co Astronomia Alec Monopoly 🔥🎨

This artist inspired timepiece features the defining works of globally renown street artist Alec Monopoly. Among them are minature sculptures of his interpretations of "The Monopoly Man" and "Scrooge McDuck," a multicolored dollar sign with multiple drawings of diamonds, and "money wings."

The process behind creating these characters begin as drawings which become CAD renderings and perfectly sized to fit inside the watch and finally cast in gold, and hand finished. 🤯

This collaboration further prooves just how versatile and innovative @Jacobandco is. From high jewelry masterpieces to collaborations with iconoc movies, hyper-cars and now internatially renown artists! 

"This is by far the smallest scale 'canvas' I have ever painted. Every element, brushstroke and color choice needed to be carefully thought out and perfectly executed," Monopoly says. "My street art murals are often free flowing and wild but given the intricacies and meticulous mechanics within these watches I needed to approach the creative process with much more precision and patience." - Alec Monopoly

What do you guys think!? #JacobAndCo #AlecMonopoly #TheBillionairesClub
